OL,3,CWarning as vision impaired people
OL,4,Creport stress and anxiety over bus
OL,5,Cstop design
OL,7,FA blind bus user has said he feels
OL,8,Funsafe and anxious using the bus stops
OL,9,Fin the city he lives in after he ended
OL,10,Fup unknowingly walking into a cycle
OL,11,Flane and a road after alighting a bus.
OL,13,FNathan Foy, from Cardiff, says he is a
OL,14,F"confident traveller", but that the
OL,15,Fdesigns of some bus stops in the city
OL,16,Fhas made getting out and about "more
OL,17,Fstressful and exhausting."
