OL,3,CWarning as vision impaired people
OL,4,Creport stress and anxiety over bus
OL,5,Cstop design
OL,7,FIt comes after a new report has warned
OL,8,Fthat people with a vision impairment
OL,9,Fand other disabilities could be losing
OL,10,Fout on their independence due to some
OL,11,Fbus stops being designed to require
OL,12,Fpeople to cross cycle lanes.
OL,14,FMr Foy told ITV Wales, "You get off
OL,15,Fthe bus and you're standing in a cycle
OL,16,Flane."
