OL,4,Creport stress and anxiety over bus
OL,5,Cstop design
OL,7,F"If, like me, you're blind and you
OL,8,Fcan't see those cyclists, you have no
OL,9,Fway of understanding the danger that
OL,10,Fyou're in, and the cyclists, they
OL,11,Fthink they're in a cycle lane.
OL,13,FHe continued: "And we have a speed
OL,14,Flimit here in Wales of 20 miles an
OL,15,Fhour. The cyclists travel a lot faster
OL,16,Fthan that, and I can't hear them
OL,17,Fcoming."
