OL,7,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said
OL,8,Fthey "recognise the design challenges
OL,9,Fwith safely routing cycle tracks along
OL,10,Fbus stops."
OL,12,FThey continued: "We will work with
OL,13,Fstakeholders to consider all available
OL,14,Fresearch in this area with a view to
OL,15,Fupdate our Active Travel Act Guidance
OL,16,Fas part of its next review, planned
OL,17,Ffor 2025."
