OL,7,FFloating island bus stops and shared
OL,8,Fbus stop boarders could be causing
OL,9,F"significant" fear, anxiety, and
OL,10,Fdistress for people with a vision
OL,11,Fimpairment and other disabilities,
OL,12,Faccording to a report from the charity
OL,13,FGuide Dogs.
OL,15,FFloating island bus stops involve a
OL,16,Fcycleway running behind the passenger
OL,17,Fboarding area at a bus stop, between
OL,18,Fan island and the footway.
