OL,7,FMeanwhile, a shared bus stop boarder
OL,8,Fis a platform onto which bus
OL,9,Fpassengers board and alight. In this
OL,10,Fsetup, a cycling track runs along the
OL,11,Fkerb ` between the footway and the
OL,12,Fcarriageway.
OL,14,FThe research, carried out by
OL,15,FUniversity College London (UCL) on
OL,16,Fbehalf of Guide
OL,18,FDogs, found that a number of people
OL,19,Fsay they have narrowly avoided
OL,20,Faccidents, leading some to avoid these
OL,21,Fbus stops altogether.
