OL,7,FThe charity says this risks limiting
OL,8,Fdisabled people's ability to live
OL,9,Findependently.
OL,11,FMr Foy said: "There are other groups
OL,12,Fof disabled people who have the same
OL,13,Fissue. So anybody using any kind of
OL,14,Fmobility getting off the bus, they're
OL,15,Fgoing to take their time crossing a
OL,16,Fbusy cycle lane.
OL,18,F"But if you think of parents with a
OL,19,Fpushchair and a pram, you're pushing
OL,20,Fthis off the bus in front of you.
