OL,7,F"You're not going to have clear sight
OL,8,Fof any cyclists that are coming, and
OL,9,Fthey have tried painting what looked
OL,10,Flike zebra crossings on there, but
OL,11,FI've never seen a cyclist observe that
OL,12,Fas a zebra crossing."
OL,14,FNathan Foy said he has been frustrated
OL,15,Fwith the rollout of these bus stop
OL,16,Fdesigns in Cardiff.
OL,18,FHe said: "These were put in without
OL,19,Fconsulting the people that are going
OL,20,Fto end up using it...
